reviewText: Clint Eastwood in the role of the spaghetti  Western. You can't get any better westerns than this!

This is the quintessential Western and the one Quentin Tarantino says is the best directed movie of all time! This version is not the epic, three-hour version with many key edited-out scenes restored, but it's more easily watched in one sitting for travelers or us ADD types. It gets all the stars!
